text: Hamal Wahab (born 9 November 1994) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Quetta in the 2012–13 Quaid-e-Azam Trophy on 25 January 2013. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Baluchistan cricketers Category:Quetta cricketers
